videos.description: In transition, Katie Lou Samuelson lobs it up and Azura Stevens tips the ball into the net.
videos.headline: Huskies' Stevens tips in the lob

videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson drains 3-pointer from the wing extending UConn's lead.
videos.headline: UConn's Samuelson knocks down easy 3

videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson drives to the hoop for the lay-in putting UConn ahead 37-12 going into halftime.
videos.headline: Samuelson drives in 27th point for UConn heading into halftime

videos.description: Gabby Williams heaves a long shot at the buzzer but is a few seconds too late.
videos.headline: Huskies' Williams drains beyond half-court shot that doesn't count
